data.description: This charming country property offers 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a detached 2 car garage on 1.476 acres of land adorned with mature trees, providing a peaceful retreat from the hustle and bustle of city life. Inside, you'll find all-new wood laminate floors that add a touch of modern elegance to the space. The primary bedroom includes a separate tub and shower, perfect for relaxation.    For those who enjoy hosting, this home features a formal dining area as well as a cozy breakfast nook, making it ideal for both intimate meals and larger gatherings. Additional amenities include a storage building for your convenience and a covered patio in the backyard, offering a great space for outdoor entertainment and relaxation.    Whether you're seeking a peaceful escape or a place to create lasting memories with loved ones, this home offers it all. Don't miss out on this opportunity to own a slice of country paradise.  Call today for a tour!
